        "created_at": "2025-03-12T03:56:45.554Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Thanks Jeremy - I always enjoy your notes. Also congrats, I can only imagine how excited you were for this tasting!</p>\n<p>Question for you - when tasting through the range do you think there is a noticeable step up from Rougeots to Genevrieres? I\u2019ve heard some people say that it\u2019s not until Perrieres that you see a noticeable step up from the village bottlings.</p>",
